PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1679356768
OL,6,FThe NUJ claims BBC management rejected
OL,7,Fproposals to trial a one-hour breakfast
OL,8,Fprogramme. The union says it believes
OL,9,F10 staff at the Derry station remain at
OL,10,Frisk of redundancy.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35004
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1679356768
OL,6,F"The announcement of a new schedule,
OL,7,Fdue to come into effect on April 24, is
OL,8,Fdeeply disappointing and leaves the NUJ
OL,9,Fwith no option but to put this matter
OL,10,Finto dispute."As a result of the strong
OL,11,Fstand taken by the NUJ and the massive
OL,12,Fpublic support for BBC Radio Foyle
OL,13,Facross the North West region, we have
OL,14,Fsucceeded in securing hourly radio
OL,15,Fbulletins and retaining the principle
OL,16,Fof a breakfast news programme on the
OL,17,Fstation. The NUJ had proposed a 1-hour
OL,18,FBreakfast Show for a trial period but
OL,19,Fmanagement has dug in on the idea of a
OL,20,F30-minute programme.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35005
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1679356768
OL,6,F"Having entered into this process in
OL,7,Fgood faith we were very disappointed
OL,8,Fwith the hard-line position taken by
OL,9,Fmanagement. We have now written to
OL,10,Fmanagement and informed them that we
OL,11,Fdispute the matter and will have to
OL,12,Fmove forward with a ballot for
OL,13,Findustrial action. There is still time
OL,14,Ffor management to reconsider its
OL,15,Fposition. The NUJ, public
OL,16,Frepresentatives and community groups
OL,17,Fmade a strong and coherent case for the
OL,18,Fretention of the Breakfast Show.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35006
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1679356768
OL,6,F"The public reaction, reflected in
OL,7,Fpetitions, meetings, rallies and
OL,8,Fparliamentary interventions, is a
OL,9,Fmeasure of the importance of BBC Radio
OL,10,FFoyle. The retention of regional
OL,11,Fbulletins and the principle that there
OL,12,Fshould be a Breakfast Show from the
OL,13,FFoyle studio are significant
OL,14,Fachievements.
OL,16,F"Having reached a measure of consensus
OL,17,Fit is entirely unreasonable to pull the
OL,18,Fplug and to announce a new, diminished
OL,19,Fschedule with a fanfare which will not
OL,20,Fsucceed in convincing anyone that this
OL,21,Fis in the best interest of BBC Radio
OL,22,FFoyle or staff.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/7
