PN,35007
SC,0007
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1679356768
OL,6,F"We will continue to campaign for a
OL,7,Fstronger commitment to Radio Foyle by
OL,8,Fthe BBC and are confident that we have
OL,9,Fthe support of the people who matter
OL,10,Fmost ` the daily listeners across the
OL,11,FNorth West."
OL,13,FIn a statement, BBC Northern Ireland
OL,14,Finterim director Adam Smyth said the
OL,15,Fchanges "reflect our commitment to
OL,16,FFoyle as a production centre for local
OL,17,Fand region-wide output".
OL,19,F"News will remain a core part of its
OL,20,Fwork, focussing on stories and issues
OL,21,Faffecting BBC audiences across the
OL,22,Fwhole of the north west," he added.
OL,3,CNUJ to ballot members for industrial
OL,4,Caction over Foyle changes
